   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "<a id='sec2-2'></a>\n",
    "## 2.2 Bin 宽度选择的影响\n",
    "\n",
    "**对应讲义**：Section 2.2 Bin 宽度的选择"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "np.random.seed(42)\n",
